After the rapper 50Cent made millions from bitcoins, another celebrity has now showed her fascination for the spark of bitcoins, that too quite overtly. The comedian and the talk show host Ellen DeGeneres spoke about bitcoins on her show recently. She says, "One thing I am down with right now, that I think everybody is learning about, is bitcoin. Who's heard of bitcoin? Who can explain what bitcoin is? Liar. Nobody knows how it works. Nobody.".
